What’s new
- Aligned clan detail member, war log, join/leave, and war stats filters
- Player profile redesign: hero header with stats panel, in-game style tabs, swipe between tabs following your finger
- Player profile now shows builder base league, best trophies, capital gold and clearer given/received donations
- Achievements tab: sub-tabs with completion counts, pending achievements listed first
- Season History: clearer stat tiles and a fixed dropdown that was invisible on Android
- Item grids (heroes, troops...) now adapt to any screen size; completion badges show a progress ring
- Android now renders real liquid glass bars (refraction, specular light) matching the iOS look
- The home to-do card now shows real account data, an all-accounts summary page, and sizes to its content
- All cards now share the same dark material and hairline border across every tab
- Player profile: new Season History tab and restyled sections, chips and progress bars
- Home event banner: correct logo per theme, tinted tiles, page dots, events sorted by next deadline
- The to-do page got a redesign: hero header with a liquid glass stats panel, cleaner account cards
- The to-do page now matches the clan detail header style and highlights the accounts that need action first
- Player cards now expand with options to enable notifications and pin an account’s to-do card to the home tab
- Player card options can now include or hide each account from the full to-do page
- The to-do page now has account search, status filters, and sorts accounts by recent activity
- Bookmarked players pinned from player card options are now included in the detailed to-do view
- The home tab now shows a single to-do card that combines the remaining tasks across all the accounts you pinned
- The account menu can now be swiped open from further inside the screen, fixing accidental app exits on Samsung devices
- Tapping a troop, spell, hero, equipment or pet now shows a detailed popup with description and stats (housing space, attack speed, range, movement speed, upgrade resource, hero and rarity for equipment)
- Item popup now shows DPS, HP/Heal at current level, targeting type (Ground/Air/Flying), and next-level upgrade cost & time
- Player item sections now show two progress percentages: current TH max-level completion and overall max-level completion
- Town-hall-maxed items now have a bronze border indicator
- Player league chips now show the league name instead of raw trophy counts
- Player profile header now shows clan identity more consistently with clan detail headers
- Player profile now shows War Stats before Achievements
- War detail now has a cleaer hero header plus redesigned statistics, events, and team sections
- War stats now use clan-style filter chips, top-level attack/defense tabs, simplified grouped war details, smoother scrolling, and improved missed-count styling
- Fixed War Stats default loading so it shows the latest 50 wars instead of a season/date-limited view
- War detail now shows clearer win-path guidance with remaining attacks, lock conditions, and opponent threat
- CWL war details now correctly count one attack per member and show win-path effort per remaining attack
- The War tab now presents account attack status without nested cards and includes opted-in bookmarked player accounts
- Fixed the CWL round banner shape on War tab cards
- Player item icons now resolve directly from ClashKing assets instead of app-data image URLs
- Seasonal event troops and spells are now hidden consistently in player progression lists
- Fixed missing player profile images for heroes, troops, spells, pets, and equipment
- Fixed startup loading so app setup errors no longer drop you into a partial session
- Fixed ClashKing deep links so player and clan links now open reliably
- Updated Turkish translations
- Some minor library updates
- Fixed bulk account loading timeouts during startup
- Improved war and clan parsing for incomplete API payloads
- Improved clan detail tabs with CWL history previews and safer loading states
- Improved clan detail filters, ranking season previews, and member donation stats
- Fixed Windows builds by avoiding incompatible fallback liquid glass shaders
